Description: Format for converting an R Markdown document to a grid oriented
  dashboard. The dashboard flexibly adapts the size of it's plots and
  htmlwidgets to the containing web page.
Imports: tools, jsonlite, htmltools, htmlwidgets (>= 0.6), rmarkdown (>= 0.9.5), shiny (>= 0.13)
